metadata.name: CryptoPunks Art Club #1
metadata.description: ***We are currently live and minting here: https://cryptopunknft.art.*** **Become a Punk.** As an Art Club member, you can own any of the 10,000 CryptoPunks, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated oil paintings.  Only one painting will be minted for each CryptoPunk, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token.  Each mint of CryptoPunk Art will be eligible for future drops of specially designed frames to highlight your fine Punk art.
